resources.description:
Cambridgeshire County Council's 2015-Based 0-19 Population Forecasts by District and Ward including Peterborough.

Forecasts are given for 2016, 2021, 2026, 2031 and 2036.
resources.name: Cambridgeshire County Council's 2015-Based 0-19 Population Forecasts by Age Group and Ward

resources.description: Cambridgeshire County Council's Research Group produces population forecasts for Cambridgeshire and Peterborough. Forecasts are provided at county, district and ward level for the years 2016, 2021, 2026, 2031 and 2036. These particular population forecasts are provided for the age group between 0-19 years in Cambridge City.
resources.name: Cambridge City 0-19 years Population Forecast 2016-2036

result.notes: This dataset is part of Cambridgeshire County Council's 2015-based population and dwelling stock forecasts. This dataset provides the population forecasts for the age group between 0-19 years. Forecasts are provided at county, district and ward level for the years 2016, 2021, 2026, 2031 and 2036.

organization.description: The Cambridgeshire Insight Partnership is made up of public, health and community bodies to provide a shared research knowledge base for the Cambridgeshire area. It allows users an easy way to access and share data, information and research for deeper insights about their local area. See more at https://cambridgeshireinsight.org.uk
